game.name: Princess Modern Job Dress Up
game.description:
Nothing could be more exciting and challenging than preparing you for an interview of a particular job! Today the two most popular Disney princesses have decided to enjoy the modern life. For this purpose, they first have to enter the corporate market. Yes, they have to find out a job at first before doing anything else. However, these princesses both are new to this domain, so they do not know how to dress them up in work style. Join Princess Modern Job Dress Up game and help them to grab a complete professional look!
Apart from guiding them to pick up a nice professional dress, you also have to help them to win their job in your own style. In this brand new dressing game for girls, you are playing the role of a career stylist whose primary responsibility is to help both the princesses to pick up the appropriate outfit for their job interview. The left side of the screen will show you the chosen princess and you can see a wide collection of dresses and makeup items on the right side of the screen. 
Choose a nice top and combine it with a matching bottom or choose a one-piece dress to give her a desired profession in this html5 girls game! Give her the best blouse, skirt and mini dress to help become the modern day lady! Do not forget to complete her look with a suitable hairstyle along with the elegant contact lenses, eye shadow, eye brow, and lipstick. Follow the same instructions for the second girl to make her look stylish yet a working woman!  Let us check what outfit would suit their personality the most! All the best to have fun with your friends, no download required!
